&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://extramojo.github.io/ExtraMojo/ExtraMojo/cli/parser/OptKind/&#34; &gt;&lt;code&gt;OptKind&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: The viable types for an option to have.&lt;/li&gt;
